AddressInfo.Title: I'Langa Mall (Nelspruit)
AddressInfo.AddressLine1: X38 Corner of Bitterbessie & Flamboyant St, West Acres
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Enter the round-about at Penny Gum Street and enter the basement parking of the centre. Use the ramps to go to the Mezanine parking level. Drive towards the Mopani Entrance. The charge point is situated to the left of the entrance.
